Dataset information:

We will clean up the data downloaded from NSW Planning Industry & Environment website (https://www.dpie.nsw.gov.au/air-quality/search-for-and-download-air-quality-data). The meteorological variables was measured hourly in three stations: 1) WALLSEND; 2) NEWCASTLE; 3) BERESFIELD. The measured 5 types of meteorological variables are: 1) Wind speed; 2) Wind direction; 3) Air temperature; 4) Relative humidity; 5) Global solar radiation.
